data.description: Hard to find a corner lot, single story 3 bed/2 bath/2 car garage home with a separate family and living room.  Kitchen has an island and stainless steel appliances.  Washer and dryer included.  So close to shopping, schools, freeway access.  Fantastic updates underway! Sellers are enhancing their space with new floors, a fresh coat of paint, and backyard makeover. Anticipated completion in just 2 weeks.  Solar provider is SunRun, soft credit pull only, and an easy transfer.  Information not guaranteed. Buyer and buyers agent to verify all information.
